**Key sections in [inference_gguf.py](file:///c:/Dev/Internship/GOVT-DOC-VLM/finetune/inference_gguf.py):**
- **§1 Model Loading** — `Llama()` with `n_gpu_layers=-1`, `n_ctx=2048`, `Llava15ChatHandler` for vision
- **§2 Image Encoding** — base64 data URI with MIME detection
- **§3 Inference** — `create_chat_completion()` with multimodal messages + `/no_think` system prompt
- **§4 Sanity Check** — hardcoded test run, prints raw output
- **§5 CLI** — `--model_path`, `--mmproj_path`, `--image_path`, `--n_ctx`, `--n_gpu_layers`

