## Next Steps (GPU Workstation)

```bash
# 1. Install llama-cpp-python with CUDA
CMAKE_ARGS="-DGGML_CUDA=on" pip install llama-cpp-python

# 2. Download model files (~17GB total)
huggingface-cli download unsloth/Qwen3.5-VL-27B-GGUF Qwen3.5-VL-27B-Q4_K_M.gguf --local-dir ./models
huggingface-cli download unsloth/Qwen3.5-VL-27B-GGUF mmproj-BF16.gguf --local-dir ./models

# 3. Run sanity check
cd finetune
python inference_gguf.py \
  --model_path ../models/Qwen3.5-VL-27B-Q4_K_M.gguf \
  --mmproj_path ../models/mmproj-BF16.gguf \
  --image_path <any_document_image.png>
```
